e-2` 的日志，确认进程异常的具体原因\n- 分析 `aiops-k8s-08` 节点的资源竞争情况\n- 检查是否存在级联故障，特别是从 `adservice-2` 到其他服务的依赖关系\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于追踪数据分析，我已经识别出系统故障期间的关键问题。以下是详细分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\", \n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice调用支付服务(paymentservice)延迟从正常13.7秒增加到77.3秒(延迟倍数5.65x)，调用邮件服务(emailservice)延迟从20.6秒增加到78.8秒(延迟倍数3.82x)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice从正常2.3-2.5秒延迟增加到9.2-13.6秒(延迟倍数4-5.5x)，前端调用购物车服务响应时间显著增加\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis操作HGET延迟从正常1.5-1.8秒增加到9.5-10.5秒(延迟倍数6-6.1x)，HMSET延迟从1.6秒增加到25.4秒(延迟倍数15.9x)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **核心延迟问题**：checkout服务在结账流程中表现最差，特别是支付和邮件发送服务调用延迟异常高\n\n2. **数据存储瓶颈**：Redis作为购物车数据存储，操作延迟显著增加，可能是导致cartservice延迟的根本原因\n\n3. **调用链传播**：故障从redis → cartservice → frontend/checkoutservice 向上传播，形成典型的依赖链故障\n\n4. **服务影响范围**：主要影响购物车和结账相关功能，产品目录服务相对正常\n\n建议进一步检查Redis集群状态和checkout服务的下游依赖（特别是paymentservice和emailservice）的健康状况。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "adservice-2 is the root cause due to pod_processes anomaly and pod_cpu_usage surge"}
